## apps

<details><summary>What are these?</summary>

These are werc apps I am involved in maintaining/contribute to, I try provide as much documentation as possible, in case my exploration can be used as someone's trail of rope

If you've never used werc and are interested I've written a [guide](../)

INSERT VIDEO FOR EDOLG

</details>

[dirdir](dirdir): _now_ a feature-rich wiki thanks to [risingthumb.xyz](//risingthumb.xyz) and slowly I

[colors](colors): visualize CSS colors

[lang](lang): translation/language-learning tools

[lights](lights): toggle on/off dark-theme

[misc](misc): not strictly an app but can be used with them

[search](search): search through files for text

[glenda](glenda): like cowsay but with [glenda](http://glenda.cat-v.org)

